(power_internal, power_logic).explanation: Power logic consumption directly contributes to the overall internal power consumption of a processor, as logic circuits are a fundamental component of internal power dissipation;

(power_internal, area_cell_area).explanation: The physical area occupied by cells directly influences internal power consumption through increased capacitance and switching activity in larger circuit areas;

(power_internal, power_register).explanation: Register file power consumption is a direct component of internal power consumption, as registers are essential internal storage elements that contribute to overall power dissipation;
